NAME

Blitz - Perl client for accessing the blitz API for performance and load
testing of cloud apps. More information on blitz at http://blitz.io

SYNOPSIS

The reference documentation for this module can be found with the perldoc

perldoc Blitz

VERSION

0.01

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Blitz

You can also look for information at:

	Github
		http://github.com/bklaas/blitz-perl
		
    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Blitz

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Blitz

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Blitz

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Blitz/


